"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block mop drugH1Div\" id=\"F135068\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Monitoring Parameters",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     With prolonged therapy, monitor hematologic, renal, and hepatic function; monitor for signs of anaphylaxis during first dose",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
